OL,7,FThe Environment Agency has launched a
OL,8,Fmajor criminal investigation to find
OL,9,Fthose responsible for illegally
OL,10,Fdumping a mountain of waste in
OL,11,FOxfordshire.
OL,13,FThe agency has been under increasing
OL,14,Fpressure to deal with the huge fly tip
OL,15,Fnear the River Cherwell in Kidlington
OL,16,Fafter local MP Calum Miller accused it
OL,17,Fof being unequipped to tackle the
OL,18,Fissue.
