OL,7,FThe "obscene" fly tip in a field
OL,8,Falongside the A34 has reached 150
OL,9,Fmetres long, 10 metres wide and 12
OL,10,Fmetres high, according to the Liberal
OL,11,FDemocrat MP for Bicester and Woodstock.
OL,13,FAt a meeting on Wednesday (19th
OL,14,FNovember), the Environment Agency
OL,15,Fspoke with the police and the local
OL,16,Fcouncil as part of its investigation.
OL,18,FHowever, a spokeswoman for the agency
OL,19,Ftold ITV Meridian it won't clear up
OL,20,Fthe waste as it's not its
OL,21,Fresponsibility.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
