OL,7,F"We don't have a statutory duty to
OL,8,Fclear waste, but we do have powers
OL,9,Fthat we can use," said Anna Burns, the
OL,10,FEnvironment Agency's Area Director for
OL,11,Fthe Thames area.
OL,13,F"We want the people who caused this
OL,14,Fpollution to pay," she explained,
OL,15,Fadding that the criminals responsible
OL,16,Fshould have to clear it up.
OL,18,FMs Burns said: "We don't want the
OL,19,Fpublic purse to have to pay for
OL,20,Fsomeone else's crime and we don't want
OL,21,Fto make it attractive to criminals.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
