OL,7,F"I completely understand why
OL,8,Fcommunities want this waste gone, it's
OL,9,Fa blight on the landscape.
OL,11,F"Our priority is to manage risk and
OL,12,Fthen pursue those responsible to make
OL,13,Fthem pay," she said.
OL,15,FMs Burns declined to specify how long
OL,16,Fit could take for the rubbish to be
OL,17,Fremoved.
