OL,7,FIt's been described as an
OL,8,Fenvironmental catastrophe by local
OL,9,Fcampaigners, who fear chemicals from
OL,10,Fthe rubbish will harm wildlife and
OL,11,Fpotentially run into the River
OL,12,FCherwell.
OL,14,FLen, a local landowner, said he saw
OL,15,Ftrucks dumping waste at the site in
OL,16,FJuly and August and couldn't
OL,17,Funderstand how it was allowed to
OL,18,Fcontinue.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
