OL,7,F"I was just dumbstruck having worked
OL,8,Fon building sites for sixty years. It
OL,9,Fhappens all the time and they just go
OL,10,Ffly-tipping anywhere now," he said.
OL,12,F"It's a criminal act and it's just
OL,13,Fgoing to go on and nobody seems to
OL,14,Fstop it."
OL,16,FSpeaking in Parliament earlier this
OL,17,Fweek, Calum Miller, MP for Bicester
OL,18,Fand Woodstock, said he was "deeply
OL,19,Fconcerned that the Environment Agency
OL,20,Fis not equipped to deal with this
OL,21,Funfolding environmental disaster."
