OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer labelled the mountain
OL,8,Fof waste as "utterly appalling", and
OL,9,Fsaid: The Environment Agency will use
OL,10,Fall available powers to make sure that
OL,11,Fthe perpetrators cover the cost of the
OL,12,Fclean-up which must now follow.
OL,14,FMr Miller has also called for the
OL,15,FGovernment to issue a directive
OL,16,Fsimilar to that for Hoads Wood near
OL,17,FAshford, Kent, in 2024 which told the
OL,18,FEnvironment Agency to clear up the
OL,19,Fsite.
