OL,7,FIn a statement, the Environment Agency
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is a sickening case of
OL,9,Flarge-scale illegal waste dumping and
OL,10,Fwe share the public's disgust.
OL,12,F"We have launched a major
OL,13,Finvestigation and are working closely
OL,14,Fwith the police and other agencies to
OL,15,Ffind those responsible and bring them
OL,16,Fto justice.
OL,18,F"Our specialist officers remain on the
OL,19,Fground to support the investigation,
OL,20,Fand monitor the site to protect people
OL,21,Fand the environment from harm."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
