OL,7,FThe agency estimates that waste crime
OL,8,Fcosts England's economy around #1
OL,9,Fbillion a year in damages.
OL,11,FCouncillor Judy Roberts, Oxfordshire
OL,12,FCounty Council's cabinet member for
OL,13,Fplace, environment and climate action,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Along with our partners, we
OL,15,Fhave been dealing with this awful
OL,16,Fenvironmental crime for several months.
OL,18,F"An incident of this scale has
OL,19,Fobviously caused considerable problems
OL,20,Ffor all parties involved.
